songs.title: De One Below
songs.lyrics:
I came to see Lynch

There's an awful that you don't know
You think you've seen everything, you haven't
There are things you've never dreamed of
There's another world out there

Nigga, I'm not scared of you

A thousand years, your order has awaited my return
Behold that you have failed
With your last breath there was EBK 4
